            <div class="p-6">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded-sm text-xs font-semibold mb-3" style="background-color: rgba(55,114,207,0.15); color: #3772cf;">Impact</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mt-2">The Power of Small Donations: How Every Contribution Makes a Big Impact</h3>
